 = Scene 1 =
 EXT. SPACE - DAY
 
 A vast starfield stretches into infinity.
 
 CAPTAIN
 All systems nominal.
 
 FIRST OFFICER
 Aye, captain. Ready for launch.
 
 The captain nods, gripping the controls.
 
 CAPTAIN
 Then let's make history.
 
 = Scene 2 =
 INT. BRIDGE - CONTINUOUS
 
 Alarms blare as the ship shudders.
 
 FIRST OFFICER
 What was that?
 
 CAPTAIN
 We've got a problem.
 
 = Scene 3 =
 INT. ENGINE ROOM - LATER
 
 Sparks fly from a ruptured conduit.
 
 JONES
 (to the engineer)
 Can you fix it?
 
 ENGINEER
 I'll try.
 
 THE END
 
